## Common Refactoring Patterns

### 1. Extract Method/Function
**Before:**
```javascript
function processOrder(order) {
  // Validate order
  if (!order.id || !order.items || order.items.length === 0) {
    throw new Error('Invalid order');
  }
  if (order.total < 0) {
    throw new Error('Invalid total');
  }

  // Calculate discount
